      "rationale": "GCI study performed on two mesh levels (coarse 4.2M cells, medium 9.8M cells); a third systematically refined mesh was not completed due to computational resource constraints. GCI estimated at 8.3% on the hemolysis index, exceeding the 5% threshold. The medium mesh was adopted for production runs based on engineering judgment that the residual discretization error is acceptable for relative comparisons. Achieved level 2 does not meet the required level 3 for this MRL 2 high-consequence COU."
    },
