    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepts the CFD model for CPB hemolysis prediction at MRL 2. Six of seven assessed factors meet required levels. The discretization error factor achieved level 2 against a required level 3; the team judges the 8.3% GCI acceptable for relative hemolysis comparisons given that the model is used to rank operating conditions rather than predict absolute hemolysis values. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) provides additional conservatism. All other factors assessed at or above required levels.",
